tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE neural_network_training_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    training_data BYTEA,
    intermediate_results JSONB,
    checkpoints JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE intermediate_results (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  result_data JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE checkpoints (
  checkpoint_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_checkpoint BYTEA
)

CREATE TABLE training_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  log_data TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE training_parameters (
  param_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  parameter_data JSONB
)

CREATE TABLE model_summary (
  summary_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  summary_data JSONB
)
